0.7.5.name: wordpress/watchmyback24
0.7.5.description: WatchMyBack24 verifies trackbacks and comments by checking against spam keywords, existing backlinks, BBCode and Hooray-Jobs with a special algorithm. WatchMyBack24 is a low traffic plugin because it doesn't check any external databases.
